    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是一个简单干脆的农村生活游戏~</h2><br>&quot;你家里是农村的，给不了我想要的生活！分手吧！&quot;<br><br>失恋的你，拖着疲惫的身躯，从大城市回到了老家农村，阳光灿烂，绿草如茵，乡亲们仍旧如你小时候一样，勤劳、朴实、善良。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/2d3d182e034d2716f47f4a7dd7980442.poster.avif?t=1722918366\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/2d3d182e034d2716f47f4a7dd7980442.webm?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/2d3d182e034d2716f47f4a7dd7980442.mp4?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“钱不钱的都没关系！人回来就好！”<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/5cbe9468a6155daf8c23fc1d339f87c7.poster.avif?t=1722918366\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/5cbe9468a6155daf8c23fc1d339f87c7.webm?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/5cbe9468a6155daf8c23fc1d339f87c7.mp4?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>嗯，也许，996并不是什么美好的人生，在老家，跟乡亲们一起建设新农村，也是一种不错的选择？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/a0cee952063bc4cb3dad537477eec376.poster.avif?t=1722918366\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/a0cee952063bc4cb3dad537477eec376.webm?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2150870/extras/a0cee952063bc4cb3dad537477eec376.mp4?t=1722918366\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏要素：<br><br>■ 脱贫攻坚，帮助家乡建设：可以收集原材料、赚取金钱，为村子里的乡亲们建造工厂、学校、牧场、医院等等基础设施，提升村里的GDP，改善乡亲们的生活！<br><br>■ 多种劳动，不怕没事干：种田、打猎、抓老鼠、抓小偷、抗击村霸黑社会、钓鱼、摸虾、抓泥鳅、采蘑菇、给孩子们代课辅导学习、帮村里老人们买米买面，帮助乡亲们脱贫致富！<br><br>■ 自由探索的世界：可以探索周围的大自然，和周边村镇，发现材料和珍奇的宝物！<br><br>■多位可以提升好感的NPC：村里有好多人，都是从小和你一起长大、或者看着你长大的，这次回乡，可以多帮帮他们，提升好感，可以解锁多种剧情！<br><br>谢谢您的游玩！：）",
